'''Nikolaï Vassilievitch Gogol''' d amyaru arusi, laṣel-is d ukrani, ilul ass n 31 meɣres 1809  di Poltava, yemmut ass n 21 furar 1852 di [[Musku]]. Yella d anaggal, d anellis, d amedyaz, am akken yura daɣen deg umezgun d uzɣan. Assa yettuneḥsab seg yimura imeqranen maḍi n teskla tarusit taklasikit. Yettwassen ugar s wungal-is meqqren "Lerwaḥ yemmuten", akked d tullist "[[Anzaren]]" i yellan dɣa s teqbaylit.



